title: Recap: Michigan State beats Indiana, 52-26
text:
Recap: Michigan State beats Indiana, 52-26 Live Blog Michigan State football vs. Indiana  ; Lansing State Journal 7:22 p.m. EDT October 24, 2015 Buy Photo MSU receiver Aaron Burbridge catches the Spartans' third touchdown of the first half past Indiana's Rashard Fant Saturday 10/24/2015. (Photo: Rod Sanford/Lansing State Journal) Buy Photo 
No. 7 Michigan State (7-0, 3-0 Big Ten) faces off against Indiana (4-3, 0-3) at 3:30 p.m. Saturday in East Lansing. 
Follow Lansing State Journal's Graham Couch and Chris Solari, Detroit Free Press' Joe Rexrode and IndyStar's Zach Osterman during the game. Also visit greenandwhite.com for more MSU coverage.
